Types of Access Specifier
private:- Same class
public:- All ove java world
protected:- All over same package (subclass and non-subclass) and different package subclass
default(Package level Access Specifier):- All over the same package (subclass and non-subclass)

        Methods                         Access Specifiers
same class                    public   protected   default  private
same package & subclass       public   protected   default
same package & non-subclass   public   protected   default
diff package & subclass       public   protected
diff package & non-subclass   public

